          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="card">
        <%= image_tag "dispatch.png", class: "img-fluid" %>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title" style="color: blue; font-weight: bolder;">2. DISPATCH</h3>
          <p class="card-text" style="font-size: 15px;">
            Attend to your other business, within  a few minutes a panasonic speed logistics personnel will
            arrive at your pickup location to pick up your package or request for delivery or execution respectively.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="card">
        <%= image_tag "delivery.png", class: "img-fluid" %>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title" style="color: blue; font-weight: bolder;">3. DELIVERY/EXECUTION</h3>
          <p class="card-text" style="font-size: 15px;">
            The Delivery of the package(s) or execution of the errands is carried with detailed precision
            and constant communication with the client. Door to Door Delivery.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="card">
        <%= image_tag "confirmation.png", class: "img-fluid" %>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title" style="color: blue; font-weight: bolder;">4. PROOF OF DELIVERY</h3>
          <p class="card-text" style="font-size: 15px;">
            Delivery competition and proof of delivery. Once is completed you will receive an email and an sms
            with the proof of delivery. The email has a signature and complete details of your order.
